# Git commit attribution

Never add any of these to commits, PR descriptions, or commit messages:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Co-authored-by: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor`

All commits must appear only under the repository owner's identity.

Before committing, verify the message has no Cursor attribution lines.
